sys.argv[1] \-> Word or a letter to be searched
.IP \(bu 2
sys.argv[2] \-> File that is to be searched
.IP \(bu 2
sys.argv[3] \-> Search option (\-\-se, \-\-sw, \-\-li, \-\-h)
